CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Heart Test Laboratories Inc is a medical technology company focused on applying innovative AI-based technology to an ECG to expand and improve an ECG's clinical usefulness. The objective of the company is to make an ECG a far more valuable cardiac screening tool, particularly in frontline or point-of-care clinical settings.
